Life Planner

Requirements:
1) Java (http://java.com/en/download/index.jsp)
2) Apache Derby (http://db.apache.org/derby/derby_downloads.html)

Setting Derby classpath:
1) Set up DERBY_HOME variable (http://db.apache.org/derby/docs/dev/getstart/tgssetupjavaenvir.html)
2) Setting up CLASSPATH (http://db.apache.org/derby/papers/DerbyTut/install_software.html#derby_verify)